     windows.show_crt_warning
     "0"
     PHP_INI_ALL
     Available since PHP 5.4.0.






&ini.descriptions.title;






    windows.show_crt_warning
    boolean




     This directive shows the Windows CRT warnings when enabled. These
     warnings were displayed by default until PHP 5.4.0.
